@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333
@refreshToken = COLE_SEU_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI

### [SUCESSO] Renovar sessão com refresh token válido
# Esperado: 200 com novo accessToken e novo refreshToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### [FALHA] Refresh token inválido
# Esperado: 401 UnauthorizedError
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "token-invalido"
}

###

### [FALHA] Refresh token ausente
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{}